name: I've Decided To Go Back (V)
Lore: '''This is your arena. I feel I must return to mine.''',
Text: 'Use 1 Force to deploy (or retrieve) non-[Virtual] Amidala, Panaka, or Ric Olie from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
